&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://neodb.social/m/item/movie/2023/08/11/ad61824a-9236-490f-9bd1-c675cb313673.jpg" alt="星条红与皇室蓝"&gt;
